 iceweasel | icedove | iceape-browser
Description: Icelandic dictionary for hunspell
 This is the Icelandic dictionary for use with the hunspell spellchecker. It
 provides spell checking capabilities in software such as Firefox and
 LibreOffice.
 .
 The spell checker is build from two sources, a wordlist and words from the
 Icelandic Wiktionary with morphological information. The wordlist was
 released into the public domain in the early nineties by Orðabók Háskóla
 Íslands & Reiknistofnun Háskóla Íslands.

